{"tid":1900558,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[客觀分析] 2020預算案會如何通過","createTime":"2020-02-27T09:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T14:02:25.000Z","uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19776056314274a99c8389f23b8d9a83b1b51d74","tid":1900558,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"大家呢兩日喺到討論個預算案，又話支持泛民投反對，我明白<br />\n不過大家都要睇下個戰場係咩情況先<br />\n我只係俾翻啲資料俾大家，唔係要撥冷水唔係要散播失敗論<br />\n反而係希望大家知己知彼<br />\n<br />\n參考翻2019年嘅預算案，你就會知投反對票只係一個表態性質<br />\n<br />\n客觀條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：目前為止立法會全體總數議席有67（3席懸空），現有非建制議席<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">23個</span></span>，建制派<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">43個</span></span>.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">議員擬提<span style=\"color: red;\">156</span>項修正案 梁君彥批<span style=\"color: red;\">56</span>項 </span></span></strong><br />\n</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190506/s00001/1557131337227/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%93%AC%E6%8F%90156%E9%A0%85%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A3%E6%A1%88-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E6%89%B956%E9%A0%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190506%2Fs00001%2F1557131337227%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258F%2590156%25E9%25A0%2585%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E6%2589%25B956%25E9%25A0%2585&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=1dfa6973\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190506%2Fs00001%2F1557131337227%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258F%2590156%25E9%25A0%2585%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E6%2589%25B956%25E9%25A0%2585&h=acaacd48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190506/s00001/1557131337227/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%93%AC%E6%8F%90156%E9%A0%85%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A3%E6%A1%88-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E6%89%B956%E9%A0%85</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">立法會三讀通過《撥款條例草案》</span></strong></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n「立法會以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">44</span></span>票贊成、<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">15</span></span>票反對，無人棄權，三讀通過......<br />\n審議期間，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">16名議員提出的56項修正案全部被否決或不獲處理</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457868-20190516.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457868-20190516.htm&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=a4364751\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457868-20190516.htm&h=91118d86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457868-20190516.htm</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年<br />\n有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">156個</span></span>修正案提出<br />\n然後要被主席審批得翻<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">56個</span></span><br />\n最後又要過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">分組點票</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">全數被否決</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2019年<br />\n建制派全投贊成已經有43個人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">佔全體一半</span></span>，達到通過所有草案門檻<br />\n政府提出嘅所有方案都會順利通過到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">預視<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n2020預算案必定通過，同2019年情況相同，泛民嘅修正案都無法通過。<br />\n<br />\n即使再次出現「等埋發叔」，成功否決到個預算案<br />\n港共仍然可以透過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">臨時撥款</span></span><br />\n日後再過錢俾警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n《立法會通過臨時撥款決議案 支付1310億元公共開支》<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448695-20190320.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448695-20190320.htm&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=13468225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448695-20190320.htm&h=f0142ad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448695-20190320.htm</a></span>"},{"pid":"488b3dacc35dbf36fc9a63012b765ccd64c0898e","tid":1900558,"uid":300435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:46:32.000Z","msg":"9月參選人立刻發動及宣傳政綱,削減驚方預算,慳返果D錢派比市民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdtdPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdtdPS</a><br />\n<br />\n既然777無恥派錢,<br />\n我地都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n<br />\n依家即刻宣傳政綱,<br />\n9月立會一過半,<br />\n就即刻發動議案,<br />\n削減驚方預算，<br />\n<br />\n驚方1年預算258億元,<br />\n削減一半就130億元,<br />\n4年立法任期就520億元,<br />\n再叫政府比D錢來,<br />\n就儲夠710億,<br />\n下年又可以派一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cb3e20ce18779eb8680c3c78f18b4dab982467","tid":1900558,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"121aba9496d62f9c345b462226216528c82d4994","tid":1900558,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:51:37.000Z","msg":"p牌仔自推"},{"pid":"6161d799a167253f75d069e04aed60d43361f789","tid":1900558,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:52:04.000Z","msg":"p牌仔自推"},{"pid":"09d357327af305fa8ada769ef7eab66bf49a8cf6","tid":1900558,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2cb3e20ce18779eb8680c3c78f18b4dab982467","tid":1900558,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"p牌仔自推"},{"pid":"961e57521af0746c0116740469be62a25cc7c039","tid":1900558,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:01:35.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"9ee64cb5c221e67eec5d3935cde1203a424fb8f9","tid":1900558,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"961e57521af0746c0116740469be62a25cc7c039","tid":1900558,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:01:35.000Z","msg":"拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"p牌仔自推"},{"pid":"87d781293e07cf1bc4ce8fa98bbc4eadd385c9af","tid":1900558,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:02:05.000Z","msg":"p牌仔自推。"},{"pid":"c969cd8389736d68fa7b35e112e71bca60b7b454","tid":1900558,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike"